      "reviews": [
        {
          "reviewTitle": "Best Tinted Moisturizer",
          "reviewText": "I have been using this product for years. I love that it is lightweight and leaves skin feeling moisturized and smooth. It has a very light coverage that creates an even skin tone but doesn\u2019t look like makeup. It balances out those variations in skin tone and redness. I use this as my base, a little bronzer for contouring and translucent setting powder for my T and it\u2019s my favorite 5 minute makeup routine! As long as you aren\u2019t rubbing your face it stays all day and doesn\u2019t settle into my wrinkles.",
          "reviewDate": "Reviewed in the United States on March 18, 2026",
