          },
          "helpfulVotes": "5 people found this helpful"
        },
        {
          "reviewTitle": "Good but off a shade",
          "reviewText": "I really like this tinted moisturizer. I have been searching for a new one since honestly company doesn\u2019t make theirs anymore. This has been my favorite one I found so far, but it is not quite the right shade for my skin tone. It works well as a foundation and blends well, and last all day. The scent is a lot odd but very mild and is not noticeable once it has been on for a few minutes. I feel like it does well at keeping my skin moist and is lightweight. I wish it was easier to find right shade or that it blended to my skin tone better. I will be trying other shades to see if I can find the right one.",
          "reviewDate": "Reviewed in the United States on July 27, 2025",
          "customer": "Laura Kate Patterson",
          "customerProfileUrl": "https://www.amazon.com/gp/profile/amzn1.account.AFTXF4YPLFRLQZQNY2OMUK7KRQ4A",
          "customerStarsRating": 4,
          "productSpecs": {
