          },
          "helpfulVotes": "10 people found this helpful"
        },
        {
          "reviewTitle": "Favorite makeup product",
          "reviewText": "The only \u201cfoundation\u201d I will use! Light enough it doesn\u2019t cover my freckles but still gives a little glow.",
          "reviewDate": "Reviewed in the United States on March 3, 2026",
          "customer": "Shae Dodge",
          "customerProfileUrl": "https://www.amazon.com/gp/profile/amzn1.account.AEMHP5MMPKEOOZAR7755F24OVFJQ",
          "customerStarsRating": 5,
          "productSpecs": {
            "color": "22S light sand"
          }
        },
        {
          "reviewTitle": "100/10 will purchase again",
          "reviewText": "I\u2019ve been searching for a tinted moisturizer that doesn\u2019t feel heavy, doesn\u2019t make me breakout, doesn\u2019t make me look shiny and doesn\u2019t pill on my skin within an hour of me having this on. I can finally say I found the perfect match. This goes on perfectly just with your fingers and gives you flawless skin, no matter what your bare skin looks like. It has not made me break out, it doesn\u2019t feel or look oily on my skin, doesn\u2019t make me look orange or pale and it doesn\u2019t pill at all. It is incredibly buildable if you want to layer some blush on top but I think it looks great without anything else. Will definitely be buying again!!!",
          "reviewDate": "Reviewed in the United States on September 22, 2025",
          "customer": "Lauren",
          "customerProfileUrl": "https://www.amazon.com/gp/profile/amzn1.account.AHSULI5JCJTBLFGXIPXMMSNVOSVA",
          "customerStarsRating": 5,
          "productSpecs": {
            "color": "10N fair neutral"
          },
          "helpfulVotes": "15 people found this helpful"
        },
        {
          "reviewTitle": "Just a Dash of Color and Coverage",
          "reviewText": "Hard to pick color online, wish I\u2019d gone a shade lighter. But it is just the right amount of coverage!!",
          "reviewDate": "Reviewed in the United States on February 19, 2026",
          "customer": "Julie A. Pribic",
          "customerProfileUrl": "https://www.amazon.com/gp/profile/amzn1.account.AFSNJBGLTSQVMVJJQNJ4JG5DMMJA",
          "customerStarsRating": 5,
          "productSpecs": {
            "color": "25N light-medium neutral"
          }
        },
        {
          "reviewTitle": "I Love it!",
          "reviewText": "I was never big on a full face of makeup. So foundation was never my thing. But I\u2019m very much into face moisturizer's, so when I started hearing about tinted moisturizer\u2019s, that was right up my ally!! I tried about 3 different brands total within the last 2 years and this one is my fav. It matches my skin tone perfectly and blends great! I typically only use it if I\u2019m going somewhere but it can totally be used daily. I like to use a natural face oil like vitamin C or E oil as my base, and then I put the tinted moisturizer on. To spice it up, I\u2019ll add some eye makeup & lip gloss & I\u2019m good to go! The moisturizer goes on smoothly and feels great! Super lightweight, gives me a little nice natural glow and it does not feel like you have anything on your face! This is my go to, it last all day and it's a great alternative for people who just want a little bit of something on but not a full face of makeup!",
          "reviewDate": "Reviewed in the United States on February 13, 2026",
